data.description: Move in ready updated home. Upon entering you will notice the new front door and see the beautiful new laminate flooring throughout. The kitchen has new wood cabinets and lovely counters.  The kitchen is large an open with plenty of cabinetry and storage. Each bathroom has a new wood cabinets with quartz counters. This house has been well maintained.  There is a lanai with access to the large fenced back yard.  Great for your pets. The roof was replaced in 2022.  New HVAC in 2018.  Located in the Jockey Club, where there is a club house, pool, tennis and basketball courts.  HOA fee is only $240 annually.
